item.title: SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Abstract
item.description: SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Abstract Datatype Description SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Abstract models a generic tracking object type. Typically a tracking object with a specific purpose has it’s own data type defined within the SoftLayer API. Local data The data recorded by a tracking object. Type: SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Data[] id A tracking object's internal identifier. Type: integer label Tracking object label Type: string resourceTableId The identifier of the existing resource this object is attempting to track.
